## **CALCULATED METRICS (IMMEDIATE, CLIENT-SIDE)**

These calculate in real-time as users enter data:

### **Calculation 1: AGI per FTE (Monthly & Annual)**

**Field Names:**

* `agi_per_fte_monthly` (calculated)  
* `agi_per_fte_annual` (calculated)

**Formulas:**

javascript  
// Requires: monthly\_agi from Financial tab  
agi\_per\_fte\_monthly \= monthly\_agi / total\_team\_size\_fte  
agi\_per\_fte\_annual \= agi\_per\_fte\_monthly \* 12  
\`\`\`

\*\*Display Format:\*\*  
\`\`\`  
AGI per FTE  
  Monthly: $18,462  ✓ Healthy  
  Annually: $221,544

**Conditional Display:** Only show if both `monthly_agi` (from Financial tab) AND `total_team_size_fte` are provided

**Benchmark Zones (Monthly):**

* \<$12,000 \= Concerning (🔴 red)  
* $12,000-$15,000 \= Acceptable (🟡 yellow)  
* $15,000-$20,000 \= Healthy (🟢 green)  
* $20,000+ \= Excellent (🟢 bright green)

**Benchmark Zones (Annual):**

* \<$144,000 \= Concerning  
* $144,000-$180,000 \= Acceptable  
* $180,000-$240,000 \= Healthy  
* $240,000+ \= Excellent

**Visual Indicator:**

* Show checkmark ✓ or colored dot next to monthly figure  
* Include benchmark label: "Healthy" / "Acceptable" / "Concerning"

---

### **Calculation 2: Billable:Non-Billable Ratio**

**Field Name:** `billable_ratio_calculated`

**Formula:**

javascript  
billable\_ratio \= billable\_staff\_count / non\_billable\_staff\_count  
\`\`\`

\*\*Display Format:\*\*  
\`\`\`  
Billable:Non-Billable Ratio  
  3.2:1  ✓ Healthy Leverage

**Special Cases:**

* If `non_billable_staff_count = 0`, display: "All billable (no support staff)"  
* If `billable_staff_count = 0`, display: "All non-billable (no delivery staff)"

**Conditional Display:** Only show if both `billable_staff_count` AND `non_billable_staff_count` are provided

**Benchmark Zones:**

* \<2:1 \= Top-heavy (🟡 yellow) "More management/support than ideal"  
* 2:1-2.5:1 \= Balanced (🟢 green)  
* 2.5:1-4:1 \= Healthy leverage (🟢 bright green)  
* 4:1 \= Very lean (🟡 yellow) "May need more support infrastructure"

**Visual Indicator:**

* Show checkmark ✓ or colored dot  
* Include benchmark label

---

### **Calculation 3: Contractor % of Workforce**

**Field Name:** `contractor_percentage_calculated`

**Formula:**

javascript  
total\_workforce \= total\_team\_size\_fte \+ average\_contractor\_count  
contractor\_percentage \= (average\_contractor\_count / total\_workforce) \* 100  
ft\_percentage \= 100 \- contractor\_percentage  
\`\`\`

\*\*Display Format:\*\*  
\`\`\`  
Contractor % of Workforce  
  13% contractors, 87% full-time  
\`\`\`

\*\*Conditional Display:\*\* Only show if \`average\_contractor\_count\` is provided (greater than 0\)

\*\*No Benchmark Zones:\*\* This is contextual — some agencies intentionally use high contractor %, others don't

